---
By: Rainer Maria Rilke
Source:
  ID: 631057a1-0221-4885-ba61-78b661b62b70
  Source:
    Description: January 4, 1923
    Title: Letter to Madame M-R
Title: White Roses
Description: June 3
---
Every day, on contemplating  these exquisite white roses, I wonder if they are
not the perfect image of the unity of being and non-being in our lives. That, I
would say, constitutes the fundamental equation of our existence.
